In this movie, Steven Seagal and Ja Rule get put in the &quot;NEW ALCATRAZ&quot; apparently because Ja Rule kills a cop. While in jail they usually have fights with the security guard, a overweight lunatic. One day a man named Donny (Morris Chestnut) infiltrates a prison with a band of crooks looking for 200 million dollars worth of US gold. One of the inmates hid it. Now the inmates are retaliating, with Seagal and Ja Rule leading them. Written by Anonymous
